description:
As this was already available on YouTube, I've combined it and added it here. It is available here, in parts: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0OK6XyFM_jw
Presentation by Dr. G. Paul Chambers on his book "Head Shot; The Science behind the JFK Assassination." JFK Lancer Conference, November 2011, President John F. Kennedy Assassination.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
